data.title: Camp Rock (DVD, 2008) Region 4 - Jonas Brothers - Good Condition - Free Postage
data.meta_description:
Camp Rock (DVD, 2008) Region 4 - Jonas Brothers - Extended Edition. Directed by Matthew Diamond and produced by Disney, this comedy movie starring the Jonas Brothers and Demi Lovato follows the story of a young girl who attends a music camp and discovers her passion for singing. The DVD is in good condition and comes with free postage.


The movie features a talented cast including Anna Maria Perez De Tagle, Alyson Stoner, and Nick Jonas. The extended edition includes a behind the scenes featurette and has a run time of 95 minutes. Language options include English and the region code is DVD: 4 (AU, NZ, Latin America...). Perfect for fans of the Jonas Brothers and anyone who loves a feel-good musical story.
